{"tid":2070280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度擬提高部份支那貨關稅","createTime":"2020-06-19T04:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T05:22:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"495c7f8591e5dded226d2cfe789881bfb78af365","tid":2070280,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"印度擬提高部份中國貨關稅<br />\n19.06.2020 12:20<br />\n<br />\n中印關係因主權爭議地區衝突而緊張，印度傳媒引述消息人士報道，印度政府正考慮提高對一系列商品的進口關稅，當中大部分是來自中國，主要針對非必需品。現時印度主要從中國進口金屬製品、鐘錶電子設備和玩具等。<br />\n<br />\n中印邊防部隊星期一在有主權爭議的加勒萬河谷地區，爆發嚴重肢體衝突。印度傳媒報道，雙方進行少將級別會談後，中方釋放事件中被扣押的10名印度士兵。有衛星照片顯示，中方近日運送機械設備，到事發的加勒萬河谷地區。有專家說，見到實際控制線兩旁有大量車輛駐守。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1313855&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1313855%26csid%3D261_341&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=3fdb6407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1313855&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"44fd0d20633693a2f721444721209f5903b65e81","tid":2070280,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"有料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6ced97096ca376215e561192d2534ac4551277","tid":2070280,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:22:29.000Z","msg":"中国侵印陣亡將士名單曝光，全世界入去致哀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2069125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2069125</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}